Seattle-area dude. 30s, liberal, lots of hair, piercings, etc. Boring he/him pronouns.

I'm into alphabetized lists, books, cooking, humor, games, not being a dick, philosophy, plants, tea, tech, ukulele, and wordplay.

#DemoTheCat and #GoblinTheCat are my overlords.

Aspiring stoic, Buddhist-adjacent, and an occasional pescetarian. Sometimes I plug my blog.

Black lives matter, fascism sucks, Fox News is a poison, patriotism is easily co-opted, and women's health belongs to women. Vote.
